237
00:14:49,333 --> 00:14:51,666
- IT'S BECAUSE I'M A VODARAC.

238
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:52,875
- HUH?

239
00:14:52,958 --> 00:14:55,166
- CAN YOU GET ME THE PEPPER
FROM OVER THERE?

240
00:14:55,250 --> 00:14:57,666
- WHAT?

241
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:59,791
- YOU SEE, IT WAS FATE
THAT I WOULD BE

242
00:14:59,875 --> 00:15:01,291
CAPTURED BY YOU
AND YOUR FRIENDS TODAY.

243
00:15:01,375 --> 00:15:03,416
- HMM.
- THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

244
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:06,541
- WELL, THEN WHY'D YOU TRY
TO RUN AWAY FROM US?

245
00:15:06,625 --> 00:15:08,625
WELL, YOU SEE, IN THIS WORLD,

246
00:15:08,708 --> 00:15:11,166
THERE ARE DESTINIES
THAT YOU MUST ACCEPT

247
00:15:11,250 --> 00:15:13,208
AND CHALLENGES
THAT YOU MUST FIGHT AGAINST.

248
00:15:13,291 --> 00:15:14,750
- I DON'T UNDERSTAND THAT
AT ALL.

249
00:15:14,833 --> 00:15:16,916
- THAT'S BECAUSE
YOU ARE NOT ONE OF THE PEOPLE

250
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,250
THAT HAVE SEEN
THE BRILLIANT LIGHT OF VODARAC.

251
00:15:19,333 --> 00:15:22,250
NOW CAN YOU HAND ME
THE CAYENNE PEPPER, PLEASE?

252
00:15:22,333 --> 00:15:23,541
- HUH?

253
00:15:23,625 --> 00:15:25,916
- IT'S THE BOTTLE
NEXT TO THE BLACK PEPPER.

254
00:15:27,791 --> 00:15:30,541
- SO WHY ARE YOU IN A COALITION
AGAINST THE GOVERNMENT?

255
00:15:30,625 --> 00:15:33,625
- OH, BRING ME THE SALT TOO.

256
00:15:33,708 --> 00:15:36,500
YOU SEE, WE REALLY
DON'T MEAN TO BE

257
00:15:36,583 --> 00:15:38,166
FIGHTING AGAINST
THE GOVERNMENT.

258
00:15:38,250 --> 00:15:39,666
- HMM?

259
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:43,166
- IT'S JUST THAT THE
ARMED FORCES THINK WE ARE.

260
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:46,333
WHEN A BIRD
IS LOCKED UP INSIDE A CAGE,

261
00:15:46,416 --> 00:15:48,916
IT DREAMS OF THE SKIES
EVERY DAY, RIGHT?

262
00:15:57,625 --> 00:16:00,250
WOULD YOU LIKE
TO TASTE IT?

263
00:16:00,333 --> 00:16:01,791
- UH, SURE.

264
00:16:10,291 --> 00:16:11,791
AHHH!

265
00:16:11,875 --> 00:16:13,416
- ( laughs )
- ( coughing )

266
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:16,083
- PERHAPS YOU'RE A LITTLE TOO
YOUNG TO BE EATING THIS FOOD.

267
00:16:16,166 --> 00:16:18,083
- I DON'T THINK
THAT'S THE PROBLEM.

268
00:16:18,166 --> 00:16:20,250
- RENTON,

269
00:16:20,333 --> 00:16:21,833
I'M RELIEVING YOU.

270
00:16:21,916 --> 00:16:24,291
- HMM.  THANKS A LOT.

271
00:16:25,916 --> 00:16:28,125
- YOU'LL GROW TO
UNDERSTAND THESE THINGS BETTER

272
00:16:28,208 --> 00:16:30,666
WHEN YOU'RE OLDER
AND BECOME AN ADULT.

273
00:16:51,416 --> 00:16:54,958
WOULD YOU LIKE TO TASTE THIS
FOR YOURSELF?

274
