FOR THOSE WHO AREN'T USED TO IT.

277
00:17:02,541 --> 00:17:05,541
- SO TELL ME
WHERE NORB IS.

278
00:17:08,625 --> 00:17:11,833
I REALLY DIDN'T WANT TO START
OUT BY USING FORCE LIKE THAT.

279
00:17:11,916 --> 00:17:13,833
BUT THE MILITARY
TOLD US THAT YOU WERE

280
00:17:13,916 --> 00:17:16,541
A VERY DANGEROUS,
ANTI-GOVERNMENT FACTION.

281
00:17:16,625 --> 00:17:18,291
I'M SORRY.

282
00:17:18,375 --> 00:17:20,250
- AND THAT WAS THE MOST
STRAIGHTFORWARD WAY

283
00:17:20,333 --> 00:17:22,416
TO HANDLE IT, CORRECT?

284
00:17:30,958 --> 00:17:32,583
- THE MONEY!

285
00:17:39,166 --> 00:17:40,541
( whistles )

286
00:17:40,625 --> 00:17:42,166
- WHAT THE HELL
DID YOU DO TO THEM?

287
00:17:42,250 --> 00:17:45,041
- NOT A THING.
- ALL RIGHT, LET'S GO.

288
00:17:59,875 --> 00:18:02,625
HMM.  ALL RIGHT!
IT'S A DEAL!

289
00:18:05,791 --> 00:18:07,166
- AH!
- WHAT THE HELL?

290
00:18:09,500 --> 00:18:11,583
- AHHH!

291
00:18:13,208 --> 00:18:17,041
WHOO-HOO!
- SHIT!  DON'T LET 'EM GET AWAY.

292
00:18:19,791 --> 00:18:22,625
- THEY'RE COMING!
- Talho: I KNOW!

293
00:18:27,208 --> 00:18:28,750
- ( gasps )

294
00:18:30,708 --> 00:18:33,583
- ALL RIGHT NOW! LET'S GIVE
'EM A HOT ONE TO CHEW ON!

295
00:18:38,791 --> 00:18:42,000
- COMMENCING ENERGY CHARGE!
HEAT RATE OF INCREASE

296
00:18:42,083 --> 00:18:43,916
IS WITHIN
THE EXPECTED PARAMETERS!

297
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:46,916
THREE, TWO, ONE,

298
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,958
FIRE!

299
00:18:54,208 --> 00:18:56,666
- ALL RIGHT! YEAH!

300
00:18:56,750 --> 00:18:59,000
WE DID IT! ( laughs )
- ( yawns )

301
00:18:59,083 --> 00:19:01,916
- ( stuttering )

302
00:19:05,541 --> 00:19:07,500
