303
00:19:07,583 --> 00:19:10,916
MAMA, YOU WERE AMAZINGLY COOL
OUT THERE!

304
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:13,000
- COOL?
- OH YEAH!

305
00:19:13,083 --> 00:19:15,000
YOU WERE REALLY REALLY COOL!

306
00:19:15,083 --> 00:19:19,041
- ( Renton gagging )

307
00:19:19,125 --> 00:19:20,583
