- I DON'T MIND.

310
00:19:26,500 --> 00:19:30,250
EVERYTHING HAPPENS IN ACCORDANCE
WITH THE WILL OF VODARAC.

311
00:19:30,333 --> 00:19:32,458
- I KNOW THIS WON'T MAKE UP
FOR EVERYTHING,

312
00:19:32,541 --> 00:19:34,625
BUT I'LL TAKE YOU
TO ANY LOCATION

313
00:19:34,708 --> 00:19:37,083
THAT YOU WANT TO GO.
- WELL THEN,

314
00:19:37,166 --> 00:19:39,708
I'LL GO
TO OUR PILGRIMAGE LAND,

315
00:19:39,791 --> 00:19:41,833
TO <i>CIUDADES DEL CIELO.</i>

316
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:50,791
- Hap: THE FACT THAT THEY WANT
THE VODARAC MORE THAN US

317
00:19:50,875 --> 00:19:52,416
