INFORMATION ABOUT US

318
00:19:52,500 --> 00:19:55,416
HASN'T MADE ITS WAY TO THE
LEADERS OF THE ARMED FORCES YET.

319
00:19:55,500 --> 00:19:56,875
- THAT'S TRUE,
BUT WE STILL CAN'T

320
00:19:56,958 --> 00:19:58,625
